==English==
===Pronunciation===
*/tʃəˈtʃɪŋ/, /tS@"tSIN/

===Etymology===
[[Onomatopoeia]] from the sound of a [[cash register]] or [[slot machine]]

===Interjection===
'''cha-ching'''
#[[Score]]!; [[Wow]]!; said to [[celebrate]] something that has made or will make lots of [[money]]

===Verb===
'''cha-ching'''
#to make a cash register or slot machine [[noise]]; to make the noise of [[coin]]s [[falling]]

===Alternative forms===
*'''chaching''', [[kerching]] (primarily UK)

